pda.control

Class PhotoBoostCtrl

  • java.lang.Object
    • pda.control.PhotoBoostCtrl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IApplication

    public class PhotoBoostCtrl
extends java.lang.Object
implements IApplication
    The PhotoBoostCtrl is the controler allowing to add the application to the PDA
    It implements IApplication and define all of the needed methods
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Florent Catiau-Tristant and Mehdi Haddad
